{"title":"[博客建设四]hexo插件配置","date":"2023-04-04T00:00:00.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"Apr 4, 2023","L":"04/04/2023","MM-DD":"04-04"},"link":"2023/04/04/[博客建设四]hexo插件配置","comments":true,"categories":["博客建设"],"updated":"2023-04-04T00:00:00.000Z","content":"<blockquote>\n<p>一些 hexo 插件的演示与具体的配置</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"cipher-加密:\">cipher 加密:<a title=\"#cipher-加密:\" href=\"#cipher-加密:\"></a></h2>\n<is-cipher placeholder=\"加密内容\">U2FsdGVkX1//UUwbUhtbRf8hBs/liZrMu3RkAdl+FwfQ4Jtf1D40q9v8msgnnxW1J94VCotzdMcjsZrMDvdOlA==</is-cipher><figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">::: cipher (●&#x27;◡&#x27;●) 加密内容</span><br><span class=\"line\">(●&#x27;◡&#x27;●)这都能被你识破</span><br><span class=\"line\">:::</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><figcaption><span>_config.inside.yml</span></figcaption><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">- cipher:</span><br><span class=\"line\">  placeholder: Passcode is required</span><br><span class=\"line\">  excerpt: Content encrypted</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"palette-调色板\">palette 调色板<a title=\"#palette-调色板\" href=\"#palette-调色板\"></a></h2>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><figcaption><span>_config.inside.yml</span></figcaption><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">- palette:</span><br><span class=\"line\">  col: 5</span><br><span class=\"line\">  theme: [</span><br><span class=\"line\">  &#x27;#673ab7&#x27;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">  &#x27;#3f51b5&#x27;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">  &#x27;#2196f3&#x27;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">  &#x27;#009688&#x27;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">  &#x27;#4caf50&#x27;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">  &#x27;#ff9800&#x27;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">  &#x27;#ff5722&#x27;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">  &#x27;#795548&#x27;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">  &#x27;#607D8B&#x27;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">  &#x27;#2a2b33&#x27;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  ]</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"bilibili-卡片\">bilibili 卡片<a title=\"#bilibili-卡片\" href=\"#bilibili-卡片\"></a></h2>\n<p>显示 b 站视频卡片的插件 <a href=\"https://github.com/MaxChang3/hexo-bilibili-card\" target=\"_blank\">link</a><br>\n<code>&#123;% bilicard your_video_id %&#125;</code></p>\n<div class=\"bvideo\"><a href=\"//www.bilibili.com/video/BV1iv4y117Fk\" target=\"_blank\">\n        <div class=\"bvideo-box\">\n            <div class=\"bvideo-cover\">\n                <div class=\"cover-default\"></div>\n                <div class=\"bvideo-cover-layer\" style=\"background-image:url(https://pic1.xuehuaimg.com/proxy/http://i1.hdslb.com/bfs/archive/aea796d934e507a3f8e10bd6ba77150b3a4e0daa.jpg)\">\n                    <i class=\"icon-video\"></i>\n                </div>\n                <span class=\"duration\">26:54:42</span>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"bvideo-info\">\n                <p class=\"title\">对于美国小学生可能过于幼稚但对于国内大学生刚刚好，多个高质量英语动画故事帮助巩固英语语法和听力</p>\n                <p class=\"card-status\">\n                    <span class=\"play-num\">\n                        <i class=\"fa fa-youtube-play\"></i>\n                        <span>113.0万</span></span>\n                    <span>\n                        <i class=\"fa fa-list-alt\"></i>\n                        <span>4193</span></span></p>\n                <div class=\"partition\">\n                    <label class=\"card-label\">视频</label>\n                    <label class=\"up-label\"></label>\n                    <label class=\"up-name\">知识共享者</label>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"actions hide\"></div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </a></div>\n<h2 id=\"clipboard-复制按钮\">clipboard 复制按钮<a title=\"#clipboard-复制按钮\" href=\"#clipboard-复制按钮\"></a></h2>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><figcaption><span>_config.inside.yml</span></figcaption><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"># 全局导入 font-awesome 字体与 jQuery,</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">- //cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/font-awesome@4.7.0/css/font-awesome.min.css</span><br><span class=\"line\">- //cdnjs.loli.net/ajax/libs/jquery/3.2.1/jquery.min.js</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">- position: [post, page]</span><br><span class=\"line\">  template: |</span><br><span class=\"line\">  &lt;script type=&quot;text/javascript&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/clipboard@2.0.4/dist/clipboard.js&quot;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  &lt;script type=&quot;text/javascript&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/s1acr/my_jsDelivr@main/clipboard.js&quot;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  &lt;link href=&quot;https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/s1acr/my_jsDelivr@main/clipboard.css&quot; rel=&quot;stylesheet&quot;&gt;  </span><br><span class=\"line\">   </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"valine-评论\">valine 评论<a title=\"#valine-评论\" href=\"#valine-评论\"></a></h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://valine.js.org/quickstart.html\" target=\"_blank\">官方文档</a></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><figcaption><span>_config.inside.yml</span></figcaption><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">- //code.bdstatic.com/npm/leancloud-storage@4.12.0/dist/av-min.js</span><br><span class=\"line\">- //unpkg.com/valine/dist/Valine.min.js</span><br><span class=\"line\">- position: comments</span><br><span class=\"line\">  template: |</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &lt;div id=&quot;vcomments&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &lt;script&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">      new Valine(&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        el: &#x27;#vcomments&#x27;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">        appId: &#x27;nppwTVm3zC7Giiu9rRKfkjkE-gzGzoHsz&#x27;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">        appKey: &#x27;PrViE3tpVOff1CMwElCVGeqB&#x27;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">        path: &#x27;window.location.pathname&#x27;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">        visitor: true,</span><br><span class=\"line\">        recordIP: true,</span><br><span class=\"line\">        admin_email: &#x27;2845391871@qq.com&#x27;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">        placeholder: &#x27;Write a Comment&#x27;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">        avatar: &#x27;retro&#x27;    </span><br><span class=\"line\">      &#125;)       </span><br><span class=\"line\">    &lt;/script&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"不蒜子访客量统计\">不蒜子访客量统计<a title=\"#不蒜子访客量统计\" href=\"#不蒜子访客量统计\"></a></h2>\n<p><a href=\"http://ibruce.info/2015/04/04/busuanzi/\" target=\"_blank\">官方文档</a></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><figcaption><span>_config.inside.yml</span></figcaption><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">footer:</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;span id=&quot;busuanzi_container_site_uv&quot; style=&#x27;display:none&#x27;&gt;Total &lt;b&gt;&lt;span id=&quot;busuanzi_value_site_uv&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt; Visitors &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span id=&quot;busuanzi_container_site_pv&quot; style=&#x27;display:none&#x27;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span id=&quot;busuanzi_value_site_pv&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt; Views&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">plugins:</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">- position: sidebar</span><br><span class=\"line\">  template: |</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &lt;script async src=&quot;https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/s1acr/my_jsDelivr@main/busuanzi.js&quot;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/s1acr/PicGoLib@main/Typora/202305011236862.png\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"φbp\"></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>本地显示的数据是不正确的, 部署完显示就正常了<br>\n这里引入的不是官方的 cdn 文件, 因为 live2D 会和不蒜子起冲突, 导致无法显示统计量.<a href=\"https://blog.csdn.net/weixin_44834205/article/details/126593378\" target=\"_blank\">参考</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"live2d\">live2D<a title=\"#live2d\" href=\"#live2d\"></a></h2>\n<p>导入模块</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ npm install --save hexo-helper-live2d</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>下载模型<br>\n参见:<br>\n可选择的模型地址: <a href=\"https://github.com/xiazeyu/live2d-widget-models\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/xiazeyu/live2d-widget-models</a><br>\nlive2D 相关的项目有很多<br>\n<a href=\"https://github.com/EYHN/hexo-helper-live2d\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/EYHN/hexo-helper-live2d</a><br>\n<a href=\"https://github.com/stevenjoezhang/live2d-widget\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/stevenjoezhang/live2d-widget</a><br>\n选择你想要的, 这里是一只黑猫 hijiki</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">npm install --save live2d-widget-model-hijiki</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><figcaption><span>_config.yml</span></figcaption><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br><span class=\"line\">26</span><br><span class=\"line\">27</span><br><span class=\"line\">28</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"># 根目录中配置</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">live2d:</span><br><span class=\"line\">enable: true</span><br><span class=\"line\">scriptFrom: local</span><br><span class=\"line\">pluginRootPath: live2dw/</span><br><span class=\"line\">pluginJsPath: lib/</span><br><span class=\"line\">pluginModelPath: assets/</span><br><span class=\"line\">tagMode: false</span><br><span class=\"line\">debug: false</span><br><span class=\"line\">model:</span><br><span class=\"line\">use: live2d-widget-model-hijiki #这里改为你模型的名字</span><br><span class=\"line\">display:</span><br><span class=\"line\">superSample: 2</span><br><span class=\"line\">position: right</span><br><span class=\"line\">hOffset: 0</span><br><span class=\"line\">vOffset: -20  </span><br><span class=\"line\"> bottom: 100</span><br><span class=\"line\">width: 150</span><br><span class=\"line\">height: 200</span><br><span class=\"line\">mobile:</span><br><span class=\"line\">show: true</span><br><span class=\"line\">scale: 0.5</span><br><span class=\"line\">react:</span><br><span class=\"line\">opacity: 0.7</span><br><span class=\"line\">opacityDefault: 0.7</span><br><span class=\"line\">opacityOnHover: 0.9</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/s1acr/PicGoLib@main/Typora/202305011234890.png\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"φbp\"></p>\n<p>有些配置不知道是组件起冲突了还是项目没有在维护的原因, 没有效果, 比如<code>opacityOnHover</code></p>\n<h2 id=\"点击颜文字特效\">点击颜文字特效<a title=\"#点击颜文字特效\" href=\"#点击颜文字特效\"></a></h2>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><figcaption><span>_config.inside.yml</span></figcaption><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"># 头像和侧边栏点击生成随机颜文字</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">- position: [avatar, sidebar]</span><br><span class=\"line\">  template: |</span><br><span class=\"line\">     &lt;script type=&quot;text/javascript&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/s1acr/my_jsDelivr@main/randomColorTextEmoticons.js&quot;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"樱花飘零特效\">樱花飘零特效<a title=\"#樱花飘零特效\" href=\"#樱花飘零特效\"></a></h2>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><figcaption><span>_config.inside.yml</span></figcaption><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"># 点击 sidebar footer 中的向日葵开启樱花飘落, 不通用, 我给#sunflower 绑定了一个事件</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">- position: sidebar</span><br><span class=\"line\">  template: |</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &lt;script type=&quot;text/javascript&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/s1acr/my_jsDelivr@main/Sakura.js&quot;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"algolia-搜索\">Algolia 搜索<a title=\"#algolia-搜索\" href=\"#algolia-搜索\"></a></h2>\n<p>作者写的很详细 <a href=\"https://blog.oniuo.com/post/integrating-algolia-search-in-theme-inside\" target=\"_blank\">link</a></p>\n","prev":{"title":"[博客建设五]inside主题Markdown样式","link":"2023/04/05/[博客建设五]inside主题Markdown样式"},"next":{"title":"[博客建设三]更换字体与美化","link":"2023/04/03/[博客建设三]更换字体与美化"},"plink":"https://s1acr.github.io/2023/04/04/[博客建设四]hexo插件配置/","toc":[{"id":"cipher-加密:","title":"cipher 加密:","index":"1"},{"id":"palette-调色板","title":"palette 调色板","index":"2"},{"id":"bilibili-卡片","title":"bilibili 卡片","index":"3"},{"id":"clipboard-复制按钮","title":"clipboard 复制按钮","index":"4"},{"id":"valine-评论","title":"valine 评论","index":"5"},{"id":"不蒜子访客量统计","title":"不蒜子访客量统计","index":"6"},{"id":"live2d","title":"live2D","index":"7"},{"id":"点击颜文字特效","title":"点击颜文字特效","index":"8"},{"id":"樱花飘零特效","title":"樱花飘零特效","index":"9"},{"id":"algolia-搜索","title":"Algolia 搜索","index":"10"}],"reward":true,"copyright":{"author":"slacr_","license":"<a href=\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src = \"/lib/cc-by-nc-sa.svg\">CC BY-NC-ND 4.0</a>","published":"April 4, 2023","updated":"April 4, 2023"},"reading_time":"854 words in 6 min"}